    <li><a href="/elaws/overtime.htm">Overtime       Security Advisor</a> &#151 helps determine       which employees are exempt from the FLSA minimum wage and overtime pay       requirements under the Part 541 overtime regulations. </li>
    <li><a href="/elaws/otcalculator.htm">Overtime       Calculator Advisor</a> &#151 computes the       amount of overtime pay due in a sample pay period based on information       from the user. </li>
